{"tid":1875644,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"四環醫藥(00460.HK)與熙德隆達合作框架 優先推進新型冠狀病毒藥物","createTime":"2020-02-12T02:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T05:34:16.000Z","uid":294550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1841b2a9d566d7c380605dac8b773d942383aaba","tid":1875644,"uid":294550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:02:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.992397/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Faastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.992397%2F2&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=6a34cf5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.992397/2</a><br />\n<br />\n四環醫藥(<a href=\"http://00460.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00460.HK&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=ddbeb496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00460.HK</a>)  +0.100 (+9.804%)    沽空 $2.43百萬; 比率 6.373%   公布，與印度熙德隆製藥達成合作框架協議，雙方合作內容包括心腦血管領域、中樞神經領域和抗感染包括新型冠狀病毒(2019 -nCoV)等領域藥品的研發、產品註冊、技術轉移、原料供應和本地化生產及銷售方面密切配合。<br />\n<br />\n數據<br />\n更新於 2020/02/12 09:17<br />\n四環醫藥<br />\n累積表現<br />\n年初至今\t +20.43%<br />\n1個月\t +21.74%<br />\n數據<br />\n更新於 2020/02/12 09:17<br />\n藥品類<br />\n同業平均累積表現<br />\n年初至今\t +29.44%<br />\n1個月\t +27.22%<br />\n<br />\n基於中國新型冠狀病毒肺炎的流行情況，協議雙方均一致同意將針對新型冠狀病毒藥物的引進、開發和生產作為首要事宜，優先推進，為中國抗擊疫情貢獻一份力量。(de/d)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 2020-02-11 16:25。)"},{"pid":"791ff5de56aaf1fcaa7896b639081bb823ee0f79","tid":1875644,"uid":294550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:11:21.000Z","msg":"鳩升中"},{"pid":"2b2dce211c6e7614b33756985d7d39e84ac46209","tid":1875644,"uid":294550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /